description:
Tamarai Honoka is http://anidb.net/ch81235 [Rena]`s best friend and the captain of the female volleyball team at their school. A naive, friendly, and sweet girl. She has noticeably large breasts which are a bit of the running gag. Having a strong aptitude and athletic ability, she felt pressure from people who can`t surpass her, which is why Rena`s claim to be her rival makes Honoka treasure their friendship. Despite being a genius at sports, she isn`t very good academically.
Source: Wikipedia
name: Tamarai Honoka
